Author: tseokii
Text: You don't have to share it with her! That might be what she's hoping for but I'm sure she still sees the therapeutic value in you just kinda assessing your habits on your own. It might give you some ideas for what you do want to say. If the thought of sharing that info with her is too much, just try going in with the assumption that you're doing this for yourself. You can decide if/how much you want to share later. <3
